title: Youta Vegetarian Food Stall
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Chinese, Thai, Fast food, Take-out
description: Look for bright yellow sign YOUTA. There's a stall near railroad and a stall near Soi 70. Youta is a chain of food stalls serving veggie food from vegetable curries and imitation fish red curry to fresh corn fritters and bananas & sticky rice cooked in a banana leaf on the charcoal bbq. Previous locations at Soi 88 and Soi 6 have both shut.
